headline: Super Micro Stock Tumbles. Why the AI Server Maker Cut Fiscal First-Quarter Revenue Guidance.
summary: Super Micro says it expects fiscal first-quarter revenue of $5 billion, down from a range of $6 billion to $7 billion.
